    "ArticleTitle": "[Usefulness of the MASCC scale in the management of neutropenic fever induced by chemotherapy in patients with solid neoplasm].",
    "Pagination": {
      "StartPage": "296",
      "EndPage": "299",
      "MedlinePgn": "296-9"
